@startuml
left to right direction

title Frontend Architecture (High-Level)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 90
skinparam ArrowColor #5A6472
skinparam ArrowThickness 1
skinparam BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam PackageBorderColor #9AA5B1
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #9AA5B1
skinparam CloudBorderColor #9AA5B1
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #9AA5B1
skinparam FolderBorderColor #9AA5B1

actor "Student" as Student

package "Browser Client" #E8F3FF {
  rectangle "App UI\nChat, Study Mode, Dashboard" as AppUI
  rectangle "Client Data Layer\nFirestore listeners + mutations" as ClientData
  rectangle "Functions Gateway\nSSE chat + study/focus calls" as FnGateway
  rectangle "Focus Engine\nremote inference + local fallback" as FocusClient #F1ECFF
  rectangle "Data Collector (/collect)" as Collector
  folder "Local Dataset ZIP\n(download export)" as ZipExport #FFF8D9

  AppUI --> ClientData
  AppUI --> FnGateway
  AppUI --> FocusClient
  ClientData --> FnGateway
}

package "Firebase Platform" #EAF7E9 {
  rectangle "Cloud Functions API" as Functions
  rectangle "Firebase Auth" as Auth #FFF8D9
  database "Firestore" as Firestore #FFF8D9
  folder "Cloud Storage\n(course materials)" as Storage #FFF8D9
}

package "External/Adjacent Services" #F2F2F2 {
  rectangle "FastAPI Inference Service\n(separate runtime)" as Inference #F1ECFF
  cloud "MediaPipe Assets\nWASM + Face Models" as MediaPipe
}

Student --> AppUI : main app flow
Student --> Collector : data collection flow

AppUI --> Auth : sign-in / sign-up
ClientData <--> Firestore : realtime reads/writes
ClientData --> Storage : material upload
FnGateway --> Functions : HTTPS calls

FocusClient --> Inference : frame stream + summary
FocusClient ..> MediaPipe : detector fallback

Collector ..> MediaPipe : calibration + labeling
Collector --> ZipExport : export run_*.zip

' keep platform nodes spread in one lane
Auth -[hidden]- Firestore
Firestore -[hidden]- Storage
Functions -[hidden]- Auth
Inference -[hidden]- MediaPipe

@enduml
